raw_text = "~ start
Broken Installer: ERROR! ERROR!
Broken Installer: Missing dependency! Missing EVERYTHING!

- Calm down
	Broken Installer: I CANNOT CALM WITHOUT libsupport.so!
- What do you need?
	Broken Installer: Package manager!
	Broken Installer: Update! Install! FIX ME!
- Ignore
	Broken Installer: SYSTEM WILL BREAK FURTHER!!!

Broken Installer: Learn how to install packages.
Broken Installer: Then maybe… I compile again.
=> END
"
